Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:10.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs15\pos(30,328)}sacrifice a sheep to a god
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:07.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}黑夜結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:12.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾所求為何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:24.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}昔日記憶殘酷嘲諷…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:33.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}撕裂黑暗的慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:38.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勿要抗拒  我深愛的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:44.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無處可藏的慾望
